5}}<br>[[Cesar Brito|Brito]]{{goal|72}}\n|location=[[Barcelona]]\n|stadium=[[Camp Nou]]\n|attendance=\n|result=L\n}}\n\n==Results==\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsed\"\n|-\n! GAMES [http://www.webdelcule.com/1899-96/1995-2000.html]\n|-\n| 20-8-1997 [[1997 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|SUPERCOPA DE ESPA\u00d1A]] BARCELONA-REAL MADRID 2-1\n\n23-8-1997 [[1997 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|SUPERCOPA DE ESPA\u00d1A]] REAL MADRID-BARCELONA 4-1\n\n\n\n15-1-1998 COPA DEL REY BARCELONA-VALENCIA 2-1\n\n22-1-1998 COPA DEL REY VALENCIA-BARCELONA 1-3\n\n5-2-1998 COPA DEL REY BARCELONA-MERIDA 2-0\n\n11-2-1998 COPA DEL REY MERIDA-BARCELONA 0-3\n\n18-2-1998 COPA DEL REY BARCELONA-ZARAGOZA 5-2\n\n26-2-1998 COPA DEL REY ZARAGOZA-BARCELONA 0-0\n\n29-4-1998 [[1998 Copa del Rey Final|COPA DEL REY FINAL]] BARCELONA-MALLORCA 1-1 /5-4/ PENALS\n\n13-8-1998 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] BARCELONA-[[Skonto FC|SKONTO]] 3-2\n\n28-8-1998 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] [[Skonto FC|SKONTO]]-BARCELONA 0-1\n\n17-9-1997 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] [[Newcastle United|NEWCASTLE]]-BARCELONA 3-2\n\n1-10-1997 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] BARCELONA-[[P.S.V. Eindhoven|PSV EINDHOVEN]] 2-2\n\n22-10-1997 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] [[Dynamo Kyiv|DYNAMO KYIV]]-BARCELONA 3-0\n\n5-11-1997 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] BARCELONA-[[Dynamo Kyiv|DYNAMO KYIV]] 0-4\n\n26-11-1997 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] BARCELONA-[[Newcastle United|NEWCASTLE]] 1-0\n\n10-12-1997 [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League|CHAMPIONS LEAGUE]] [[P.S.V. Eindhoven|PSV EINDHOVEN]]-BARCELONA 2-2\n\n8-1-1998 [[1997 UEFA Super Cup|UEFA SUPER CUP]] BARCELONA-[[Borussia Dortmund|BORUSSIA DORTMUND]] 2-0\n\n11-3-1998 [[1997 UEFA Super Cup|UEFA SUPER CUP]] [[Borussia Dortmund|BORUSSIA DORTMUND]]-BARCELONA 1-1\n\n24-3-1998 [[Copa Catalunya|COPA CATALUNYA]] LLEIDA-BARCELONA 1-2\n\n5-